				<outline text="The shaggy professor who cannot speak. https://t.co/zb53n7Yi1l" type="tweet" created="Wed, 30 Jun 2021 15:43:46 GMT" tweetId="1410262795950739456" urltweet="https://twitter.com/KenSmith/status/1410262795950739456" tweetUserName="KenSmith" />
				<outline text="Understanding blogging. Dave Winer's prompt and my reply.

https://t.co/5NZ32HQDw6

...it is about the unfinished business of making sense of our lives. We all need help in that area, if we can get it, although some people believe or pretend otherwise... https://t.co/XIfNuC0waO" type="tweet" created="Wed, 30 Jun 2021 15:33:54 GMT" tweetId="1410260312322887686" urltweet="https://twitter.com/KenSmith/status/1410260312322887686" tweetUserName="KenSmith" />
